Class OpenCLShallowParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.cqse.check.framework.shallowparser.framework.ShallowParserBase<EGenericParserStates>

          • eu.cqse.check.framework.shallowparser.languages.opencl.OpenCLShallowParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IShallowParser

    public class OpenCLShallowParser
extends CppShallowParser
    Shallow parser for OpenCL C/C++. Supports all features of CppShallowParser. Further it recognizes OpenCL specific keywords and supports parsing block literal expressions.
